# TypeScript / React Native Standards

- Strict mode (`"strict": true`). No `any`.
- Functional components only. No class components.
- Use `StyleSheet.create` for all styles — no inline style objects.
- Minimum 48px touch targets on all interactive elements.
- Use `react-native-safe-area-context` (`SafeAreaView` with `edges` prop) on every screen.
- Brand colors must come from `src/lib/colors.ts` — no hardcoded hex values in components.
